data.description: **LOCATION LOCATION**FULLY REMODELY  home with spacious living areas NEW DECK, NEW ROOF.TOTALLY  NEW KITCHEN and NEW FULL 3 BATHROOMS . Hardwood floors one the first floor including bedrooms. Smart lighting. Relax in the renovated sun room; use it as an office or gym. Detached two car garage with spacious backyard. No HOA and great access to anywhere in North Dallas and beyond with nearby HW 75, Interstate 635, Dallas North Tollway and President George Bush Turnpike.
